type.description:
## Collided Horizontally

---


[Entity Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/entity_condition_types/collided_horizontally)

Checks whether the entity is colliding horizontally (walking against a block).

Type ID: `origins:collided_horizontally`

---

### Examples
```json
"condition": {
    "type": "origins:collided_horizontally"
}
```
